    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（ベスト4をかけたクォーターファイナルまで）\n（あと一週間）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(The quarter-finals‚ which will determine the Top 4‚)\n(is in just one week.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.47588393441562,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 5.95
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（……こんな気持ちでさくらと話したら、余計な不安を）\n（与えてしまいそうだ。今日は早々に帰ろう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(If I talk to Sakura‚ feeling the way I am right now‚ I’ll only cause)\n(unnecessary worry. I’ll just go home early today.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.200000000000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "？？？",
      "speakerNameEn": "？？？",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "…………うぅ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mm…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.396231035814218,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（小屋の隅に、うずくまっている影を見つけた）\n（それは今にも消え入りそうな影だった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I find a huddled silhouette in the corner of my room.)\n(It’s a silhouette that looks like it might disappear any second.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.105936245546268,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 24.210947422609262
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……麻奈か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that you‚ Mana?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.210947422609262,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}くん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.94799960496579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 27.19146898431137
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s the matter?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.19146898431137,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03-mna003.m4a",
      "text": "…………なんでも……ない……\n心配しなくても大丈夫。ちょっと眠いだけ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s… nothing.\nDon’t worry about me. I’m just a little sleepy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.86264810008362,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 38.92931476675029
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03-mna004.m4a",
      "text": "はは……変だな……なんか、体が重くて……\n幽霊なのにね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha… How strange. My body feels kinda heavy.\nEven though I’m a ghost.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.86264810008361,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "おい、大丈夫なのか……？\n体が……床に沈んでるぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa‚ are you okay?\nYou’re sinking… into the floor.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.84627611878071,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03-mna005.m4a",
      "text": "はは……本当だ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha‚ wow‚ I really am.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.98190571051521,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03-mna006.m4a",
      "text": "なんか……前にも、こんなことあったよね……\n私が病気になって、イベント中止になりかけた時……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Didn’t something like this happen before?\nWhen I got sick‚ and we almost had to cancel an event.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.294105223632656,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ああ……撤収間際にお前が病院から抜け出してきて\n結局イベントをやる羽目になって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I remember. Right before we withdrew you from the event‚ you dashed out of the hospital‚\nand wound up doing the event anyway.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.13850410363756,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さんにこっぴどく怒られたんだぞ\nアイドルを監督出来てないって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mr. Saegusa was furious.\nHe said I wasn’t a good idol manager.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.22158795576972,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 81.25657674055975
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03-mna007.m4a",
      "text": "……だって……お客さんが……待ってるから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… the audience was… waiting for me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.25657674055975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "まあ、俺は怒られながらも少し尊敬してたけどな\nあんなに熱があるのに歌うなんて、プロだなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though I was mad at you‚ I still respected you for it.\nSinging with a high fever like that… now that’s a pro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.53952491662584,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_heart-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 100.1061915832925
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 100.1061915832925
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03-mna008.m4a",
      "text": "はは……それ、よく言われたけど……\nプロってね、本当は誰でもなれるんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hahaha. Yeah‚ I heard that a lot.\nThe thing about being a pro… is that anyone can do it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.50619158329252,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことないだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s no way that’s true.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.2561919647622,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 113.34698562206505
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03-mna009.m4a",
      "text": "なれる。だって、私の歌を\n本気で楽しみに待っててくれる人がいるんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it is. I mean‚ so many people\nare genuinely excited to hear my song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.31365228873175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 128.48031895539842
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03-mna010.m4a",
      "text": "私に会うのを本気で楽しみにしてくれる人がいるんだよ\n……そんな人がいたら、誰だって、頑張れるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And so many people are genuinely excited to see me.\nHaving that support… I don’t care who you are—it pushes you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.48031895539842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "…………そうかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe you’re right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.31365228873184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 135.35689490220634
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03-mna011.m4a",
      "text": "誰かが本気で自分を待っててくれることなんて\n生きてる中であんまりないから。だからしないだけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How often do you have someone truly eager to see you?\nIt doesn’t happen many times in life.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.2568949022065,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 147.8837886421959
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03-mna012.m4a",
      "text": "自分を楽しみに待っててくれる人がいたら\n誰だって頑張れる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But if you have someone waiting‚ someone truly excited to see you‚\nanyone will push themselves to greatness.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.8837886421959,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 150.973451560199
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03-mna013.m4a",
      "text": "だって、それは……素敵なことだもん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And that’s just… such a beautiful thing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.973451560199,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "えっ……麻奈……麻奈？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana? Mana?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.10828155821534,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 161.81966466253974
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "（いきなり、麻奈の体が光に包まれた）\n（そして霧が消えていくように、麻奈の姿が消え始める）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Suddenly‚ Mana is enveloped in light.)\n(And like dissipating fog‚ Mana vanishes.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.0196646625397,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "（その瞬間、遠くから歌声が響いた）\n（それはさくらの歌声だった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(The next moment‚ I hear a song ringing in the distance.)\n(It’s Sakura’s voice.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.9916829362111,
      "sfxList": []
